  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To verify the exact location of cuff of the endotracheal tube in children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The exact location of the cuff of the endotracheal tube in children has not been studied.
      This study is the first attempt to verify the position of the cuff in the airway with
      relation to cricoid.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
